leadingComments.value:
*
 * Date Date String
 * (M)(d)12(h)24(H)(m)(s)(E)(q)  1-2 
 * (y) 1-4 (S) 1 ( 1-3 )
 *
 * @function
 * @memberof Fx
 * @param {Date} date  Date 
 * @param {String} format 
 * @returns {String}
 * @example
 *
 * const current = new Date('2020/10/06 10:10:10');
 * // -> 2020-10-06 10:10:10'
 * console.log(Fx.formatDate(current, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss'));
 * // -> 20201006 101010
 * console.log(Fx.formatDate(current, 'yyyyMMdd hhmmss'));
